

INSTALACION DE MONGODB MACOX

-Instalar HOMEBREW en caso de no tenerlo
https://brew.sh/index_es
/usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"

-Verificar que version se tiene de HOMEBREW
# brew --version

-Instalacion de MONGODB
# brew tap mongodb/brew
# brew install mongodb-community@4.2

-Ejecutar mongodb https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/tutorial/install-mongodb-on-os-x/
# brew services start mongodb-community@4.2
# mongod --config /usr/local/etc/mongod.conf --fork
# ps aux | grep -v grep | grep mongod

PARA MANEJAR MONGODB
-Instalacion robo 3T
https://robomongo.org/download


INSTALACION DE EXPRESS

-Instalar EXPRESS
# npm i express --save

-Instalar body-parse
# npm i body-parse --save

